additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children. When undiluted, causes serious eye damage, skin irritation and may cause an allergic skin reaction. Avoid contact with eyes and skin. Do not swallow. Rinse packaging before recycling. Store below 30C. For advice, please contact a Poisons Information Centre (Phone Australia 13 11 26 or New Zealand 0800 764 766) or a doctor. If in eyes, wash out with a large amount of water. If irritation persists, contact a doctor. If you have unusually sensitive skin or a serious skin condition, please consult your doctor before using this product.
